short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A browser extension to view UKI result data in a more user-friendly way.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Gives you many useful ways to view your dog's scores:

Titles:
- Calculates IAC, IWAC, CSS, WCSS titles (and their multiples).
- Calculates Bronze, Silver, Gold Games/Agility/Jumpers titles.
- Shows scores that contributed to each title.
- Displays timeline of all titles earned.
- Shows scores you need to earn your next titles!

Qualifying Scores:
- Shows qualifying runs for US Open, Canadian Open, and West Coast Open. So you know what you need and can fill out the forms when you enter.

Multiple Record Groups:
- Score listings by dog sorted by date, by class, or by height
